item.title: CVE-2022-36929|2024-08-03T10:21:31.978Z -- zoom%20video%20communications%20inc -- zoom%20rooms%20for%20windows
item.description: The Zoom Rooms Installer for Windows prior to 5.12.6 contains a local privilege escalation vulnerability. A local low-privileged user could exploit this vulnerability during the install process to escalate their privileges to the SYSTEM user.

item.title: CVE-2022-36930|2024-08-03T10:21:31.958Z -- zoom%20video%20communications%20inc -- zoom%20rooms%20for%20windows
item.description: Zoom Rooms for Windows installers before version 5.13.0 contain a local privilege escalation vulnerability. A local low-privileged user could exploit this vulnerability in an attack chain to escalate their privileges to the SYSTEM user.
